content:encoded:
I am super excited to have been invited as a guest on another live show. The #PirateBroadcast with Russ Johns. It will be happening January 15, 2021 at 8:00am Central Time. I would love to have you stop by if you are available. I will be talking more about my latest project, The Example Show and what I am working on in 2021. Plus, I would love to hear your questions. I hope you can join us.

Topics to be discussed:

  • Data Science
  • What I am doing with The Example Show in 2021
  • Livestreaming
  • Why Content Creation is so important right now
